---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Arc^ Project — Pollutant Degradation" description="Pollutant Degradation investigates plasma-activated water for breaking down contaminants. See current hypotheses and collaboration needs.">
  <section class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-6 py-20">
    <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.4em] text-arkup-teal">Project concept</p>
    <h1 class="mt-2 text-4xl font-semibold">Pollutant Degradation</h1>
    <p class="mt-6 text-muted">
      How effectively can plasma-activated water degrade industrial and agricultural pollutants without introducing new toxicity? We’re mapping candidate effluents, reaction pathways, and verification methods.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-6 pb-16">
    <div class="grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-2">
      <div class="space-y-4 rounded-3xl border border-white/10 bg-white/5 p-6 text-sm text-muted">
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white">Project status</h2>
        <ul class="space-y-2">
          <li><span class="font-semibold text-white">Stage:</span> Idea exploration</li>
          <li><span class="font-semibold text-white">Needs:</span> Chemists, environmental scientists, data modelers</li>
          <li><span class="font-semibold text-white">Data:</span> Literature scan + baseline pollutant datasets</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="space-y-4 rounded-3xl border border-[#ffb703]/30 bg-[#ffb703]/10 p-6 text-sm text-[#ffeec7]">
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white">Safety snapshot</h2>
        <p>
          Hazard matrix under development. Expect focus on by-product gases, handling of contaminated substrates, and disposal of treated effluents.
        </p>
        <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.4em]">Formal template coming soon</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-6 pb-20">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white">Immediate next steps</h2>
    <ul class="mt-6 list-disc space-y-3 pl-6 text-muted">
      <li>Compile open-access research on PAW pollutant degradation pathways.</li>
      <li>Define environmental impact metrics (toxicity assays, energy cost per litre, lifecycle analysis).</li>
      <li>Draft pilot experiment concepts with community labs and university partners.</li>
    </ul>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
